OL,3,CThird senior figure at Gloucestershire
OL,4,CPolice suspended
OL,6,FThe chief of staff at Gloucestershire
OL,7,FPolice has been suspended pending an
OL,8,Finvestigation into alleged gross
OL,9,Fmisconduct.
OL,11,FGary Thompson was due to be issued
OL,12,Fwith a gross misconduct notice by the
OL,13,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,14,Fon 7 October - the same day as the
OL,15,FChief Constable Rod Hansen.
OL,17,FMr Hansen is currently being
OL,18,Finvestigated by the the Independent
OL,19,FOffice of Police Conduct (IPOC) for
OL,20,Falleged gross misconduct in relation
OL,21,Fto a member of staff.
