OL,6,FThe investigation centers on the
OL,7,Fhandling, by both individuals, of an
OL,8,Fallegation of computer misuse and a
OL,9,Fpotential data breach by another
OL,10,Fmember of staff.
OL,12,FThe probe will work out whether
OL,13,Frelevant policies and procedures were
OL,14,Fsubsequently followed.
OL,16,FTheir suspension does not necessarily
OL,17,Fmean any disciplinary action will
OL,18,Ffollow.
