OL,6,FThis comes just days after it was
OL,7,Frevealed Gloucestershire Police's
OL,8,FDeputy Chief Constable Shaun West was
OL,9,Fsuspended from the force in January
OL,10,Famid allegations of misconduct. He
OL,11,Fthen retired from the force in June.
OL,13,FIt has since been confirmed that Mr
OL,14,FWest is the subject of a criminal
OL,15,Finvestigation over alleged assaults
OL,16,Fand misconduct in a public office.
