OL,6,FOn the subject of Thompson and Hansen,
OL,7,Fan IOPC spokesperson said: "In respect
OL,8,Fof our investigation into the Chief
OL,9,FConstable of Gloucestershire
OL,10,FConstabulary, we can confirm a gross
OL,11,Fmisconduct notice has now also been
OL,12,Fserved on a senior member of staff at
OL,13,Fthe force.
OL,15,F"The investigation concerns the
OL,16,Fhandling by both individuals of an
OL,17,Fallegation of computer misuse and a
OL,18,Fpotential data breach by another
OL,19,Fmember of staff, and whether relevant
OL,20,Fpolicies and procedures were
OL,21,Fsubsequently followed.
