OL,6,F"The investigation follows referrals
OL,7,Fin August from the Office of the
OL,8,FPolice and Crime Commissioner for
OL,9,FGloucestershire and the police force.
OL,11,F"Such notices do not necessarily mean
OL,12,Fany disciplinary proceedings will
OL,13,Ffollow. Our investigation is ongoing."
OL,15,FA Gloucestershire Constabulary
OL,16,Fspokesperson also confirmed a senior
OL,17,Fmember of police staff has been
OL,18,Fsuspended while an investigation into
OL,19,Fan allegation of gross misconduct is
OL,20,Fundertaken.
