OL,6,FThey said it is being led by the IOPC
OL,7,Fand is linked to the misconduct
OL,8,Fallegation against Mr Hansen.
OL,10,F"We can confirm a senior member of
OL,11,Fpolice staff has been suspended while
OL,12,Fan investigation into an allegation of
OL,13,Fgross misconduct takes place.
OL,15,F"The investigation is being led by the
OL,16,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,17,Fand is linked to the inquiry into a
OL,18,Fgross misconduct allegation against
OL,19,FChief Constable Rod Hansen."
