OL,6,FAn OPCC spokesperson said: "Police and
OL,7,FCrime Commissioner Chris Nelson has
OL,8,Fbeen getting on with the important job
OL,9,Fof securing an interim Chief
OL,10,FConstable, Maggie Blyth, who he has
OL,11,Fjust announced will start work with
OL,12,Fthe Constabulary on Tuesday (October
OL,13,F22)".
OL,15,FMr Thompson has declined to comment.
OL,16,FHe said: "I do not wish to make any
OL,17,Fcomment at the moment, thank you."
